Segment Intelligence in Data Cloud

Segment Intelligence is a data-driven app that empowers customers to better use existing segments and increase the impact of their marketing activity. Segment Intelligence combines Data Cloud and CRM Analytics to surface insights on segments across multiple channels, engagement types, and conversion sources, such as revenue from Commerce Cloud. Build and enhance segments with actionable performance insights and improve your marketing return on investment (ROI) with more relevant audiences and campaigns.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience	Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions

Segment Intelligence analyzes segments, based on Unified Individuals, that are created and activated from Data Cloud to various engagement channels. You can connect up to four data sources, Marketing Cloud Engagement data (mandatory), Google Ads, Meta Ads, and Commerce Cloud data. For a more comprehensive analysis, we recommend connecting at least two of these data sources.

Set Up Segment Intelligence
Setting up Segment Intelligence involves several steps that you complete sequentially. The setup page guides you through the process of connecting first and third-party data and indicates which steps are required. To get the most comprehensive view of your data, also complete the recommended steps.
Select a Data Space to Organize Your Segment Intelligence Data
Select a data space to organize your data, metadata, and processes into categories, such as brand, region, or department. You can then limit users to see and analyze data only within the context of their category in the dashboard
Set Up First-Party Data for Segment Intelligence
Gain insights on your data by connecting your first-party data to segment Intelligence. All steps in this section are mandatory and must be completed for a successful installation.
Set Up Third-Party Data for Segment Intelligence
Connect your third-party data to view your campaign delivery and performance metrics in the Segment Intelligence dashboard.
Installation Prerequisites
Complete the installation prerequisites to install Segment Intelligence.
Set Up Data Aggregation for Segment Intelligence
To use the Segment Intelligence app and gain insights on aggregated data, select the data model objects for data aggregation and the segment attributes.
Create the Segment Intelligence Dashboard
After you complete the Segment Intelligence setup configurations, you install to create a prebuilt dashboard of your defined data. You can’t change the data after you install. To make changes, uninstall and reinstall Segment Intelligence.
